Welcome. You can use this tablet to anonymously provide feedback about your experience and satisfaction with services during your visit today. Your feedback will be used to improve services and patient experiences. This feedback form is made available to you by Cambodia's National Centre for HIV, Dermatology, and STI (NCHADS) and its partners.
Do you want to provide your feedback?
Indicate yes or no to the following statements about your recent visit to this facility.
7a. The clinic hours were convenient for me?
9a. I am not worry staff gossiped about me?
10a. The staff kept my information confidential?
1b. Reproductive health services or antenatal care
1c. How much time does it take you from where you live to reach this facility? (Tick one)
2c. How long have you been attending this health facility for HIV/AIDS treatment? (Tick one)
3c. Why do you access HIV services at this particular facility? (Multi-answers)
4c. Would you recommend this health facility to your HIV positive acquaintances or friends?
5c. Please score the facility / care / service during TODAY's visit for each of these statements (tick one box):
5c1. You felt physically safe and secure in the facility
5c2. The staff treated me disrespectful during your visit
5c3. The nurses gave you good and easy to understand information about your health and treatment.
6c. What do you suggest to improving services at this facility? Reply with a short response. (Multi-answers)
8c. How do you describe your gender today?
9c. Who do you have sex with? (Multi-answers)
10c. Have you ever had exchange sex for money or goods?
11c. Have you ever injected drugs recreationally or without a doctor's prescription?
12c. Do you want to receive free and confidential sexual health and HIV info via SMS?
13c. Could we contact you for further discussion
14c. Could you give your mobile phone number?

ស្វាគមន៍៖ តើអ្នកអាចប្រើប្រាស់កុំព្យូទ័របន្ទះស្តើង (Tablet) ដោយមិនបញ្ចេញឈ្មោះ ដើម្បីផ្តល់មតិយោបល់ត្រឡប់ពីបទពិសោធន៍និងការពេញចិត្តក្នុងកំឡុងពេលអ្នកមកទទួលសេវានៅថ្ងៃនេះដែរឬទេ? មតិយោបល់របស់អ្នកនិងយកទៅដើម្បីកែលម្អសេវាសំរាប់អ្នកជំងឺ? ទម្រង់ផ្តល់មតិយោល់ព័ត៌មានត្រទ្បប់នេះរៀបចំឡើងដោយ មជ្ឈមណ្ឌលជាតិប្រយុទ្ធ នឹងជំងឺអេដស៍ សើស្បែក និងកាមរោគ (NCHADS) និងកិច្ចសហការណ៍ជាមួយអង្គការដៃគូ ។
